 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# $C_3$ and $C_6$ Coefficients"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%pip install -q matplotlib numpy pairinteraction\n",
    "\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pairinteraction.real as pi\n",
    "from pairinteraction import perturbative"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "if pi.Database.get_global_database() is None:\n",
    "    pi.Database.initialize_global_database(download_missing=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Example to calculate the angular dependence of the $C_3$ coefficient"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ket1 = pi.KetAtom(\"Rb\", n=61, l=0, j=0.5, m=0.5)\n",
    "ket2 = pi.KetAtom(\"Rb\", n=62, l=1, j=1.5, m=0.5)\n",
    "\n",
    "c3_obj = perturbative.C3(ket1, ket2)\n",
    "\n",
    "c3_obj.set_diamagnetism_enabled(False)\n",
    "c3_obj.set_magnetic_field([0, 0, 20], \"gauss\")\n",
    "\n",
    "c3_obj.set_minimum_number_of_ket_pairs(2_000)\n",
    "c3_obj.set_interaction_order(3);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "c3_coeffs = []\n",
    "thetas = np.linspace(0, np.pi, 20)\n",
    "for theta in thetas:\n",
    "    c3_obj.set_angle(theta, unit=\"radian\")\n",
    "    c3_coeffs.append(c3_obj.get(unit=\"planck_constant * GHz * micrometer^3\"))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x500 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "\n",
    "axs[0].scatter(thetas, c3_coeffs, label=\"perturbative C3\")\n",
    "axs[0].plot(\n",
    "    thetas,\n",
    "    -0.5 * c3_coeffs[0] * (1 - 3 * np.cos(thetas) ** 2),\n",
    "    label=r\"$1-3\\cos(\\theta)^2$\",\n",
    ")\n",
    "axs[0].legend()\n",
    "axs[0].set_xlabel(r\"$\\theta$ [rad]\")\n",
    "axs[0].set_ylabel(r\"$C_3$ [$h$ GHz $\\mu m^3$]\")\n",
    "\n",
    "axs[1].remove()\n",
    "axs[1] = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 2, projection=\"polar\")\n",
    "axs[1].scatter(\n",
    "    np.append(thetas, thetas + np.pi),\n",
    "    np.append(c3_coeffs, c3_coeffs),\n",
    ")\n",
    "axs[1].plot(\n",
    "    np.append(thetas, thetas + np.pi),\n",
    "    -0.5 * c3_coeffs[0] * (1 - 3 * np.cos(np.append(thetas, thetas + np.pi)) ** 2),\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Example to calculate the angular dependence of the $C_6$ coefficient"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ket = pi.KetAtom(\"Rb\", n=61, l=0, j=0.5, m=0.5)\n",
    "c6_obj = perturbative.C6(ket, ket)\n",
    "\n",
    "c6_obj.set_diamagnetism_enabled(False)\n",
    "c6_obj.set_magnetic_field([0, 0, 20], \"gauss\")\n",
    "c6_obj.set_minimum_number_of_ket_pairs(2_000)\n",
    "c6_obj.set_interaction_order(3);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "c6_coeffs = []\n",
    "thetas = np.linspace(0, np.pi, 20)\n",
    "for theta in thetas:\n",
    "    c6_obj.set_angle(theta, unit=\"radian\")\n",
    "    c6_coeffs.append(c6_obj.get(unit=\"planck_constant * GHz * micrometer^6\"))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x500 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "\n",
    "axs[0].scatter(thetas, c6_coeffs, label=\"perturbative C6\")\n",
    "axs[0].legend()\n",
    "axs[0].set_xlabel(r\"$\\theta$ [rad]\")\n",
    "axs[0].set_ylabel(r\"$C_6$ [$h$ GHz $\\mu m^6$]\")\n",
    "\n",
    "axs[1].remove()\n",
    "axs[1] = fig.add_subplot(1, 2, 2, projection=\"polar\")\n",
    "axs[1].scatter(\n",
    "    np.append(thetas, thetas + np.pi),\n",
    "    np.append(c6_coeffs, c6_coeffs),\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  }
 ],
